---
title: Practice Onboarding — User Flow
---

flowchart TD
    Start([Practice admin begins onboarding]) --> NPI[Enter NPI Number]
    NPI --> Lookup{NPPES Lookup}
    Lookup -->|Found| Show[Display practice name,<br/>address, specialty, providers]
    Lookup -->|Not Found| Retry[Show error · retry]
    Retry --> NPI

    Show --> Confirm{Correct?}
    Confirm -->|No| NPI
    Confirm -->|Yes| Config_Start[AI begins configuration chat<br/>Sidebar: 6 areas · validated captions<br/>Nonsense → clarify or specialist]

    Config_Start --> Q1[Patient Demographics<br/>Age groups served]
    Q1 --> Q2[Prescribing Focus<br/>Drug categories, generics vs brand]
    Q2 --> Q3[Prior Auth Setup<br/>Payers, auto-submission prefs]
    Q3 --> Q4[Sample Management<br/>Categories, delivery preference]
    Q4 --> Q5[Coverage & Affordability<br/>Copay cards, PAP defaults]
    Q5 --> Q6[Provider Roles<br/>Permissions for PA, samples]

    Q1 -.->|Admin clicks sidebar| Revise[Revise previous area]
    Q2 -.->|Admin clicks sidebar| Revise
    Q3 -.->|Admin clicks sidebar| Revise
    Q4 -.->|Admin clicks sidebar| Revise
    Q5 -.->|Admin clicks sidebar| Revise
    Revise -.-> Q1

    Q3 -.->|Multi-location or EMR mentioned| Escalate
    Q6 --> Check{Escalation<br/>needed?}
    Check -->|No| Complete[CONFIGURATION COMPLETE<br/>Show summary + sidebar]
    Check -->|Yes| Escalate[Escalation banner<br/>Schedule specialist call]

    Escalate --> Continue[Continue configuring<br/>what AI can handle]
    Continue --> Q1

    Complete --> Dashboard[Go to Dashboard]
    Complete --> Schedule[Schedule walkthrough call]

    style Start fill:#E3F2FD,stroke:#1565C0,color:#000
    style Complete fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#2E7D32,color:#000
    style Escalate fill:#FFFBEB,stroke:#F59E0B,color:#000
    style Dashboard fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#2E7D32,color:#000
    style Revise fill:#EFF6FF,stroke:#2563EB,color:#000
    style Check fill:#FCE4EC,stroke:#C62828,color:#000
